CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1945, p. 15, reads: "On The Campus - This is one of the better aspects at the University of Pittsburgh. Left to right: Betsy Sachs, Olivia King, and Lois Berstein catch a bit of the remaining Indian summer as they make the job of getting a higher education an easier task.-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Betsy Sachs wearing dark jacket with plaid trim, Olivia King, and Lois Berstein seated on grass outside of Cathedral of Learning, University of Pittsburgh, Oakland
